<lb ed="I" n="0113c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0113c0101">蓋前劫莫初。心路非始。攸哉<note n="0113004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨗿＝邈【史】</note><note n="0113004" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨗿【佛拓】，邈【史】</note><app n="0113004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨗿</rdg></app>乎。靡測<note n="0113005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30720"/>＝其【史】</note><note n="0113005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30720"/>【佛拓】，其【史】</note><app n="0113005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">其</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30720"/></rdg></app>源者也。自天地<note n="0113006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30721"/>＝替【史】</note><note n="0113006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30721"/>【佛拓】，替【史】</note><app n="0113006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">替</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30721"/></rdg></app>成。陰陽啓運。□靈
<lb ed="I" n="0113c02" type="honorific"/>起滅。業報相依。莫不染習<note n="0113007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30726"/>＝色【史】</note><note n="0113007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30726"/>【佛拓】，色【史】</note><app n="0113007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">色</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30726"/></rdg></app>塵。驚馳愛慾。循環五趣。亦沉溺四流。雖<note n="0113008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30712"/>＝復【史】</note><note n="0113008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30712"/>【佛拓】，復【史】</note><app n="0113008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30712"/></rdg></app>緣起一
<lb ed="I" n="0113c03" type="honorific"/>生。受神□識。形心電速。念念□留。假使靈芝九轉。行極四誠。奔□月以高昇。<note n="0113009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30722"/>＝望【史】</note><note n="0113009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30722"/>【佛拓】，望【史】</note><app n="0113009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30722"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0113c04" type="honorific"/>玄宮而蹔息。猶亦<note n="0113010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30723"/>＝退【史】</note><note n="0113010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30723"/>【佛拓】，退【史】</note><app n="0113010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">退</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30723"/></rdg></app>沒三塗。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">旋</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">還</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">六</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">道</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">不</unclear>說<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">生</unclear>死之因緣。詎云<note n="0113011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30724"/>＝解【史】</note><note n="0113011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30724"/>【佛拓】，解【史】</note><app n="0113011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">解</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30724"/></rdg></app>脫之果報。能
<lb ed="I" n="0113c05" type="honorific"/>仁悟迹前機。超□後際。降靈□室。□□□□□□駕四門。卻遺三殿。一心高蹈。
<lb ed="I" n="0113c06" type="honorific"/>成无上尊。至<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">於</unclear>化動<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">十</unclear>方。迴□三□。吞□大<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">海</unclear>。□納須<note n="0113012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢏏＝彌【史】</note><note n="0113012" resp="ihp" type="mod">𢏏【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0113012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢏏</rdg></app>。雖神照冥通。至德潛
<lb ed="I" n="0113c07" type="honorific"/>衍。莫不稱相<note n="0113013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30627"/>＝取【史】</note><note n="0113013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30627"/>【佛拓】，取【史】</note><app n="0113013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">取</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30627"/></rdg></app><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">益</unclear>。□物□□。□□□之□。□真實之相。因化城以蹔止。演眾妙
<lb ed="I" n="0113c08" type="honorific"/>於鷲山。及<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">慧</unclear>日□□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">法</unclear>□□□。□□五□。□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">屬</unclear>三千。藉有作之功。會無為之力。
<lb ed="I" n="0113c09" type="honorific"/>航法<note n="0113014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">舩＝船【史】</note><note n="0113014" resp="ihp" type="mod">舩【佛拓】，船【史】</note><app n="0113014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">船</lem><rdg wit="【原】">舩</rdg></app>於淨□。□常<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">樂</unclear>□□□。□□天<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">人</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">慕</unclear>感。<note n="0113015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30725"/>＝像【史】</note><note n="0113015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30725"/>【佛拓】，像【史】</note><app n="0113015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">像</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30725"/></rdg></app>法興靈。惟敬真顏。寄存寶<app type="star" corresp="#0113007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">色</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30726"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0113c10" type="honorific"/><note n="0113016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30727"/>＝然【史】</note><note n="0113016" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30727"/>【佛拓】，然【史】</note><app n="0113016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">然</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30727"/></rdg></app>州武猛從<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">事</unclear>汲郡□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">六</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">鄉</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>秀老。遂割損<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">家</unclear>資。率諸<app type="star" corresp="#0113001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邑</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30728"/></rdg></app>義五百餘
<lb ed="I" n="0113c11" type="honorific"/>人。竝著信情<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">源</unclear>。崇宗□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">千</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">劫</unclear>。故正順一時。起津梁於生滅之<note n="0113017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">囦＝淵【史】</note><note n="0113017" resp="ihp" type="mod">囦【佛拓】，淵【史】</note><app n="0113017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">囦</rdg></app>。運<note n="0113018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB09274"/>＝舟【史】</note><note n="0113018" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB09274"/>【佛拓】，舟【史】</note><app n="0113018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舟</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB09274"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0113c12" type="honorific"/><note n="0113019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">檝＝楫【史】</note><note n="0113019" resp="ihp" type="mod">檝【佛拓】，楫【史】</note><app n="0113019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">楫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">檝</rdg></app>於貪慾之海。通四衢□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">駕</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">擁</unclear>三彰。竭八倒之流。兼義冠<note n="0113020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30729"/>＝鄉【史】</note><note n="0113020" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30729"/>【佛拓】，鄉【史】</note><app n="0113020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鄉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30729"/></rdg></app>閭。譽聞<note n="0113021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">邫＝邦【史】</note><note n="0113021" resp="ihp" type="mod">邫【佛拓】，邦【史】</note><app n="0113021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">邫</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0113c13" type="honorific"/><app type="star" corresp="#0113001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邑</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30728"/></rdg></app>。莫不尚祇<note n="0113022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">薗＝園【史】</note><note n="0113022" resp="ihp" type="mod">薗【佛拓】，園【史】</note><app n="0113022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】">薗</rdg></app>而結<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">慕</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">同</unclear>□□□歸依。遂瞻影天竺。尚想□城。眷茲一山。僉共
<lb ed="I" n="0113c14" type="honorific"/>嘉力。<app type="star" corresp="#0113005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">其</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30720"/></rdg></app>峻壁單懸。遙<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">峰</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">疊</unclear>□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">流</unclear>□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">野</unclear>。帶□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">山</unclear>□。至如寶塔五層。則浮空曜晷。
<lb ed="I" n="0113c15" type="honorific"/><note n="0113023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30645"/>＝金【史】</note><note n="0113023" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30645"/>【佛拓】，金【史】</note><app n="0113023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30645"/></rdg></app>棠百刃。則撫日承天。□木□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">地</unclear>□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">足</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">並</unclear>雀離之高妙矣。又真儀應<app type="star" corresp="#0113015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">像</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30725"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0113c16" type="honorific"/>則暉暎龕室。神光照<note n="0113024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">爤＝爛【史】</note><note n="0113024" resp="ihp" type="mod">爤【佛拓】，爛【史】</note><app n="0113024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">爛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">爤</rdg></app>。則□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">太</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">清</unclear>。□空隱現。無<app type="star" corresp="#0113008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30712"/></rdg></app>等級。威神相好。不可思議。
<lb ed="I" n="0113c17" type="honorific"/><app type="star" corresp="#0113008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30712"/></rdg></app>即石以拓玄<note n="0113025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30731"/>＝基【史】</note><note n="0113025" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30731"/>【佛拓】，基【史】</note><app n="0113025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">基</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30731"/></rdg></app>。因木而架□□。引長廊而交暎。接戶<note n="0113026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">牗＝牖【史】</note><note n="0113026" resp="ihp" type="mod">牗【佛拓】，牖【史】</note><app n="0113026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">牖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">牗</rdg></app>以相經。堂廡霞舒。階
<lb ed="I" n="0113c18" type="honorific"/>墀綺合。雲生枅向。風出<note n="0113027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30732"/>＝簷【史】</note><note n="0113027" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30732"/>【佛拓】，簷【史】</note><app n="0113027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">簷</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30732"/></rdg></app>軒。花□秀美。光開七淨。泉流藻注。鴻澧八<app type="star" corresp="#0113011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">解</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30724"/></rdg></app>。雖謝菩
<lb ed="I" n="0113c19" type="honorific"/>提吉祥之勝地。方同竹<app type="star" corresp="#0113022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】">薗</rdg></app>伽藍之妙哉。於<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">是</unclear>名僧德眾。煙<note n="0113028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">雧＝集【史】</note><note n="0113028" resp="ihp" type="mod">雧【佛拓】，集【史】</note><app n="0113028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">集</lem><rdg wit="【原】">雧</rdg></app>如林。栖息<note n="0113029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢦶＝戒【史】</note><note n="0113029" resp="ihp" type="mod">𢦶【佛拓】，戒【史】</note><app n="0113029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">戒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢦶</rdg></app>藏之
<lb ed="I" n="0113c20" type="honorific"/>門。優遊正定之路。結漏永消。脫諸塵網。般若之力既充。所作之功亦辨。六時精
<lb ed="I" n="0113c21" type="honorific"/>苦。不閑日夜。四事奉給。無<note n="0113030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">朁＝替【史】</note><note n="0113030" resp="ihp" type="mod">朁【佛拓】，替【史】</note><app n="0113030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">替</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朁</rdg></app>所須。而樹福良田。脩功淨土。亡情投<note n="0113031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨋎＝軫【史】</note><note n="0113031" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨋎【佛拓】，軫【史】</note><app n="0113031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">軫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨋎</rdg></app>。<app type="star" corresp="#0113013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">取</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30627"/></rdg></app>會將來。
<lb ed="I" n="0113c22" type="honorific"/>既事光<note n="0113032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠀍＝世【史】</note><note n="0113032" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠀍【佛拓】，世【史】</note><app n="0113032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">世</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠀍</rdg></app>上。業<app type="star" corresp="#0113003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩕃</rdg></app>寰中。鴻名盛德。方傳不朽。祇掌寄言。雖不盡意。題表<app type="star" corresp="#0113023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30645"/></rdg></app>石。<app type="star" corresp="#0113005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">其</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30720"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0113c23" type="honorific"/>能已哉。乃作銘曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0113c24" type="honorific"/>心塗<note n="0113033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30736"/>＝眇【史】</note><note n="0113033" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30736"/>【佛拓】，眇【史】</note><app n="0113033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">眇</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30736"/></rdg></app>極。性緒攸玄。三才始運。一<note n="0113034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30737"/>＝氣【史】</note><note n="0113034" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30737"/>【佛拓】，氣【史】</note><app n="0113034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">氣</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30737"/></rdg></app>□延。虛成報果。妄結因緣。有形分段。无<app type="star" corresp="#0113007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">色</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30726"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0113c25" type="honorific"/>已遷。於唯大覺。隨感現身。<note n="0113035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30742"/>＝權【史】</note><note n="0113035" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30742"/>【佛拓】，權【史】</note><app n="0113035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30742"/></rdg></app>影昏俗。混相纓塵。汎茲永夜。濟彼長津。緣乖化<note n="0113036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">隠＝隱【史】</note><note n="0113036" resp="ihp" type="mod">隠【佛拓】，隱【史】</note><app n="0113036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">隱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">隠</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0113c26" type="honorific"/>卷跡歸真。<app type="star" corresp="#0113032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">世</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠀍</rdg></app>崇遺教。<note n="0113037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30738"/>＝瞻【史】</note><note n="0113037" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30738"/>【佛拓】，瞻【史】</note><app n="0113037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瞻</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30738"/></rdg></app><note n="0113038" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30744"/>＝圖【史】</note><note n="0113038" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30744"/>【佛拓】，圖【史】</note><app n="0113038"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30744"/></rdg></app>影則。寶<note n="0113039" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠛴＝剎【史】</note><note n="0113039" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠛴【佛拓】，剎【史】</note><app n="0113039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠛴</rdg></app>層巖。<app type="star" corresp="#0113023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30645"/></rdg></app>槃累<note n="0113040" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30745"/>＝飾【史】</note><note n="0113040" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30745"/>【佛拓】，飾【史】</note><app n="0113040"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">飾</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30745"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0113027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">簷</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30732"/></rdg></app>宇高臨。長楹峻極。庭流
<lb ed="I" n="0113c27" type="honorific"/>桂水。<app type="star" corresp="#0113022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】">薗</rdg></app>開淨<app type="star" corresp="#0113007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">色</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30726"/></rdg></app>。既曰福地。實唯淨土。息<app type="star" corresp="#0113036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">隱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">隠</rdg></app><note n="0113041" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">桒＝桑【史】</note><note n="0113041" resp="ihp" type="mod">桒【佛拓】，桑【史】</note><app n="0113041"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">桑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">桒</rdg></app>門。淹留<note n="0113042" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30746"/>＝緇【史】</note><note n="0113042" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30746"/>【佛拓】，緇【史】</note><app n="0113042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">緇</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30746"/></rdg></app>旅。功不虛<note n="0113043" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30739"/>＝棄【史】</note><note n="0113043" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30739"/>【佛拓】，棄【史】</note><app n="0113043"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">棄</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30739"/></rdg></app>。果不妄袪。
<lb ed="I" n="0113c28" type="honorific"/>德標千劫。聲傳万古。
<lb ed="I" n="0113c29" type="honorific"/>維大<note n="0113044" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30740"/>＝魏【史】</note><note n="0113044" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30740"/>【佛拓】，魏【史】</note><app n="0113044"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">魏</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30740"/></rdg></app>永熙二年歲在甲寅興建。至武定元年歲次癸亥八月功就。仰為
<lb ed="I" n="0113c30" type="honorific"/>皇家。願國祚永<note n="0113045" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30741"/>＝延【史】</note><note n="0113045" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30741"/>【佛拓】，延【史】</note><app n="0113045"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">延</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30741"/></rdg></app>化隆遐劫。<note n="0113046" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">壃＝疆【史】</note><note n="0113046" resp="ihp" type="mod">壃【佛拓】，疆【史】</note><app n="0113046"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">疆</lem><rdg wit="【原】">壃</rdg></app>靜境安。民寧道澤。法界有形。等成正覺。</p>
